Google's Verified Boot reference implementation (versions 1.x & 2.x)
and helper tools.

Tools included:
 - cgpt, utility to read/write/modify GPT partitions with support for
Chrome OS extensions.
 - futility, used to create, sign, and validate Chrome OS images.
 - crossystem (optional), Chrome OS firmware/system interface utility.

  If you want to build the crossystem tool (used at chromebook 
platforms) set CROSSYSTEM=yes, this requires chromeos-flashrom
package.
